Text: Couldn't get this app to work properly. It says it cannot patch ? Any solutions ?

make sure the program is closed...or the file being patched will be in use and can't be overwritten.

close from task manager as it starts automatically after install completes
sorry also forgot :D ... if you are in win Vista or win7 right click patch and run as admin
